# Private Libraries

This directory is reserved for future project-specific PlatformIO libraries.

本目录预留给未来的项目私有 PlatformIO 库。

The current firmware has no private local libraries. External dependencies are declared in `Firmware/platformio.ini`; currently the main external dependency is `Adafruit NeoPixel`.

当前固件没有本地私有库。外部依赖在 `Firmware/platformio.ini` 中声明，目前主要外部依赖是 `Adafruit NeoPixel`。
